        {
            "title": "興田邨爆炸｜不尋常氣體洩漏警重案組調查 拘捕52歲男戶主",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/7411ac715973a1156e5510f1dca67937/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250310/_2025031014040118127.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>藍田興田邨美田樓一單位於上周一（3日）發生煤氣洩漏引起爆炸，冷氣機及窗框被炸開飛墮地面，大門鐵閘遭炸飛至走廊，52歲姓劉男戶主一度傷勢危殆，其後好轉。消防認為有不尋常情況導致漏氣，觀塘警區重案組跟進案件，經進一步調查後相信劉與案有關，並於上周五（7日）在油麻地區，以涉嫌「導致相當可能會危害生命或財產的爆炸」將他拘捕。劉已獲准保候查，須於4月上旬向警方報到。<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057294/即時-港聞-興田邨爆炸-不尋常氣體洩漏警重案組調查-拘捕52歲男戶主",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-10 14:06:11",
