            "title": "元朗地產舖遭淋潑紅油 疑被欠債老闆友連累",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"地產舖玻璃門被淋上紅油。楊偉亨攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/71ed3d29262bc6e3bc332e76a3f8a641/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250310/_2025031013493545788.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">地產舖玻璃門被淋上紅油。楊偉亨攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>元朗盈福街11號洪福樓地下，今（10日）早上11時46分，職員報案指一間地產公司遭淋潑紅油。警方接報到場，地舖的玻璃門被淋上2米乘1米的紅油，警將案件列刑毀處理。  \n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129043/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"地產舖玻璃門被淋上紅油。楊偉亨攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3ab500046ca4df5b6528df6a84efbef3/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250310_133201704_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        地產舖玻璃門被淋上紅油。楊偉亨攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129044/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"地產舖男女職員在場協查。楊偉亨攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f372cd3759cb09220b38d7061bb8ad6a/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250310_133201704_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        地產舖男女職員在場協查。楊偉亨攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129045/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"地產舖玻璃門被淋潑紅油。楊偉亨攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a395e6ad447cd4efe93b35f37e155aea/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250310_133201704_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        地產舖玻璃門被淋潑紅油。楊偉亨攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129046/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員到場調查。楊偉亨攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1f8ae8ee1dcab9463784e589b56b70e6/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250310_133306621_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員到場調查。楊偉亨攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129048/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0fb58911d38629078b2ac5772c6f695b/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250310_133306621_07.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129050/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"門外貼有大字報。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/252c3c8672a3f1b0797478a8fd492fe5/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250310_133306621_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        門外貼有大字報。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>地產舖門外貼有一張附有英文名的大字報「叫我黎（嚟）整你」，據了解，大字報上的英文名是地產舖老闆的朋友，該人與外人有金錢糾紛，涉款數萬元。警方相信有人未還錢被追債，對方得悉欠債人為該地產舖老闆的友人，因而找上門，金錢糾紛不涉及地產舖，地產舖屬無妄之災。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057290/即時-港聞-元朗地產舖遭淋潑紅油-疑被欠債老闆友連累",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-10 13:51:23",
            "source": "stheadline",
