            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "香港金融科技周及StartmeupHK創業節十周年 擬11月聯合舉行",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"香港金融科技周及StartmeupHK創業節十周年 擬11月聯合舉行\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f893477be67d4e633de3fb3fc18dbd3f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250310/_2025031013295165512.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">香港金融科技周及StartmeupHK創業節十周年 擬11月聯合舉行</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>投資推廣署今日宣布，為慶祝兩大旗艦盛事香港金融科技周和StartmeupHK創業節於2025年踏入十周年，兩項活動將於11月3日至7日在香港會議展覽中心及其他地點聯合舉行。\n\n</p><h2>去年初創企業增長10%</h2>\n<p>投資推廣署表示，兩項活動的結合將打造一個更具規模、全方位聚焦創科領域及商業效益的業界平台；而香港作為頂尖的國際金融中心和蓬勃的初創企業中心，致力加快數字經濟發展進程，去年初創企業數量增長便達10%，當中金融科技界別佔比例最高，共有逾600家相關初創企業。\n\n</p>\n<p>隨着金融服務及不同行業更廣泛應用科技，今年活動將打破科技領域界限，揭示如人工智能、區塊鏈、綠色科技和健康科技等尖端技術如何與香港享譽全球的金融服務及更多行業深度融合，不僅為創新與合作提供更廣闊的舞台，還提升了金融機構的競爭力，推動它們邁向未來。<br/>\n <br/>\n投資推廣署署長劉凱旋更表示，這場盛會不僅標誌着香港十年來的創新歷程，還充分融合科技並提升經濟影響力，是展現香港未來發展的重要象徵。<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057287/即時-財經-香港金融科技周及StartmeupHK創業節十周年-擬11月聯合舉行",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-10 13:41:26",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "元朗公路貨車七人車相撞 七人車車頭起火冒濃煙 司機乘客跳車逃生",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"七人車車頭着火冒濃煙。網上圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/fa914e306d07c79f7e4b747a69539ed5/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250310/_2025031013300953618.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">七人車車頭着火冒濃煙。網上圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> 元朗公路近灰沙圍，今（10日）中午12時30分，一部七人車與密斗貨車相撞後，七人車車頭着火，冒起濃濃黑煙，升上半空。七人車司機及乘客跳車逃生，消防接報到場，出動一喉一煙帽隊撲救，約13分鐘將火救熄，事件中無人受傷。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129014/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"車頭冒出濃濃黑煙，升上半空。網上圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/686aac5a17a914b999d73f88ad78afbd/2025-03/1f522816-40f4-4630-88aa-1bddf822c646.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        車頭冒出濃濃黑煙，升上半空。網上圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129015/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"車頭近車胎位置着火。網上圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3b04bbd0394c20b425ae953e351dbd0c/2025-03/3fff6005-ff70-40bc-92ab-a0e70252fd19.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        車頭近車胎位置着火。網上圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129016/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"七人車冒出濃煙。網上圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3766013a7230ce8a704207089043dd04/2025-03/43f966f4-807f-4971-aef6-a8bb34b2804a.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        七人車冒出濃煙。網上圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129017/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"網上圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ab6de246adf94722661265d0752c2caa/2025-03/446a8ae5-3f1a-4e2e-862d-b9a9d50adc05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網上圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129018/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"網上圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9cdee521013cea15a156ebb196f663b3/2025-03/534950c7-6f90-445d-9d74-e78e313c2836.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網上圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129019/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/275c3d438c1867e352b9734b027e8db9/2025-03/a02682d7-c93d-425d-83c6-2156213d9727.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129020/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黑煙升至半空。網上圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1e2dc4967727da8d505d1ab5dba8817a/2025-03/cebb7f3c-d23e-4719-a170-087460e995ac.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黑煙升至半空。網上圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>運輸署宣布，因車輛着火，元朗公路(往上水方向)近唐人新村的部分行車線現已封閉。駕駛人士只可使用餘下行車線行車。現時上址交通繁忙。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
