        {
            "title": "小天瑜死忌｜天瑜爸爸開記招 籲警方及律政司重啟調查 否則考慮提私人檢控",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"小天瑜死忌｜天瑜爸爸開記招 籲警方及律政司重啟調查 否則考慮提私人檢控\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/564a81333a03dacde51f5853bdbe1754/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250310/_2025031013260582586.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">小天瑜死忌｜天瑜爸爸開記招 籲警方及律政司重啟調查 否則考慮提私人檢控</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>【小天瑜/周天瑜/醫療事故】「小天瑜」女童周天瑜2020年疑因醫療事故成植物人，去年3月離世，惟律政司決定不就案件展開刑事檢控。今日（3月10日）是天瑜死忌，周父與大律師陸偉雄召開記者會。陸偉雄稱，事件涉公眾利益，籲律政司及警方重啟調查，交代調查方向，透露會視乎檢方回應考慮進行私人檢控。\n\n</p><h2>小天瑜死忌｜陸偉雄：事件涉公眾利益</h2>\n<p>2018年，時年3歲的周天瑜確診惡性腫瘤橫紋肌肉瘤。她2020年5月在瑪麗醫院手術期間疑遭遇醫療事故，延遲48分鐘輸血，長時間缺氧成為植物人。天瑜父母曾就事件向醫管局提出民事索償，於2023年達成和解協議，但繼續追究刑事責任。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4128988/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"周父與大律師陸偉雄召開記者會。黃偉強攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8ecfcb9407dd55fe3679f944dc0f72a5/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250310_122525121.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        周父與大律師陸偉雄召開記者會。黃偉強攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4128989/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5c7e4b96e5e423f74bfbb976b384bdd1/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250310_122525121_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4128990/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/930245909eb662c6d53b494e3ffb3fbc/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250310_122525121_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4128991/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bd554c260cf6738919db89719e20e396/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250310_122525121_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4128992/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/24549625b432b56333c9dd6ff85cac84/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250310_124046706.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129005/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"早前由警務處發出的信件，當中提及「律政司認為本案沒有合理機會致使任何人士被法庭定罪，因此不會就此案展開刑事檢控程序」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b9b28ac73e3d12d874381c97b6810c55/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250310_124046706_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        早前由警務處發出的信件，當中提及「律政司認為本案沒有合理機會致使任何人士被法庭定罪，因此不會就此案展開刑事檢控程序」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129006/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"大律師陸偉雄協助周父，向警方發信。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ef1ebfff8e0d94bdd7ad56792abe94d7/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250310_124046706_07.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大律師陸偉雄協助周父，向警方發信。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>周父去年就懷疑醫生涉篡改手術紀錄報案，他本月初在「天瑜醫療事故關注組」facebook專頁發文稱，律政司決定不展開刑事檢控。根據專頁附上的由警務處發出的信件，當中提及「律政司認為本案沒有合理機會致使任何人士被法庭定罪，因此不會就此案展開刑事檢控程序」。信件亦指，「由於此案將來有可能於死因庭進行研訊，本處（警務處）正跟進相關事宜，現時並沒有其他資料提供」。\n\n</p>\n<p>記者 蕭博禧\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057286/即時-港聞-小天瑜死忌-天瑜爸爸開記招-籲警方及律政司重啟調查-否則考慮提私人檢控",
